324
00:28:52,439 --> 00:28:54,316
CLARKIN:
They were members of a cult.

325
00:28:56,902 --> 00:29:00,748
We've confirmed that it was Higgins'
daughter and her boyfriend.

326
00:29:01,698 --> 00:29:05,168
- You may have heard on the news...
