360
00:31:09,284 --> 00:31:11,412
They are gonna love you.

361
00:31:12,245 --> 00:31:13,713
I love you.

362
00:31:14,539 --> 00:31:15,665
I love you too.

363
00:31:26,176 --> 00:31:30,522
<i>I realize, Miss Prentice, but you still
have time. Mind if I look around?</i>

364
00:31:44,403 --> 00:31:46,747
<i>But wouldn't you be more comfortable
sitting down?</i>

365
00:31:49,366 --> 00:31:51,619
