366
00:31:51,785 --> 00:31:54,163
MAN <i>[ON TV]:
I do know how painful this must be for you.</i>

367
00:32:02,587 --> 00:32:05,181
<i>Look, it had absolutely nothing
to do with the money!</i>

368
00:32:10,220 --> 00:32:13,850
<i>Look, I don't even want to talk about it.
I don't wanna think about it. I...</i>

369
00:32:15,976 --> 00:32:17,398
<i>Why don't you just leave now.</i>

370
00:32:17,561 --> 00:32:19,609
<i>What if they're not dead?
What'll you do then?</i>

371
00:32:19,771 --> 00:32:22,570
<i>I told you, I don't know!
Would you please leave?!</i>

372
00:32:24,359 --> 00:32:26,453
