374
00:33:13,033 --> 00:33:14,159
MIA:
Help me!

375
00:33:16,786 --> 00:33:18,413
[COUGHS]

376
00:33:19,414 --> 00:33:21,212
[GASPS THEN GROANS]

377
00:33:34,513 --> 00:33:35,560
[SCREAMS]

378
00:33:38,850 --> 00:33:41,273
