390
00:34:27,732 --> 00:34:29,075
Leah?

391
00:34:29,776 --> 00:34:31,870
Leah. Hi.

392
00:34:32,654 --> 00:34:34,702
Hi, Leah, it's your daddy.

393
00:34:37,075 --> 00:34:38,327
Look at her.

394
00:34:39,286 --> 00:34:40,538
Look at her.

