402
00:35:00,223 --> 00:35:04,103
I can never go back there. I can't.
I can't, not with her. No.

403
00:35:05,186 --> 00:35:06,813
You don't have to.

404
00:35:07,230 --> 00:35:08,356
Even

405
00:35:29,044 --> 00:35:31,046
[LEAH CRYING]

406
00:35:52,442 --> 00:35:54,194
Come on, come on.

