417
00:36:31,648 --> 00:36:34,527
Mia, she's fine.
Okay? You both need to get out of here.

418
00:36:34,693 --> 00:36:37,742
- You've been cooped up in here too much.
- I know, but it's...

419
00:36:37,904 --> 00:36:39,281
