444
00:38:08,745 --> 00:38:11,123
Ah, yes. Sure, of course.

445
00:38:11,289 --> 00:38:13,417
No, no, no. Hold her on your lap.

446
00:38:14,167 --> 00:38:15,965
Oh, you don't need me in the photo.

447
00:38:16,336 --> 00:38:17,383
Of course I do.

